Package com.flipfit.bean

Class BaseUser

java.lang.Object
com.flipfit.bean.BaseUser
Direct Known Subclasses:
Customer, GymOwner, SystemAdmin
public abstract class BaseUser extends Object
BaseUser is an abstract class that provides the common attributes for all types of users in the FlipFit system, such as User, SystemAdmin, and GymOwner. It encapsulates shared properties like user ID, name, email, and password.
